welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Warendorf, Germany! Get ready to fall in love with our charming city, known for its rich history, beautiful architecture, and friendly locals. We invite you to immerse yourself in our culture and explore all that Warendorf has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"
